    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一款关于梦之投影的休闲怀旧解谜游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进房间，从架子上取下玩具，摆放在桌面上，创造趣味投影。随着游戏的深入，你将重温温馨的家庭回忆，周围的环境也会随之变化，让幻想与现实的界限逐渐模糊。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/76b4fd3dcadf8ab097293c669fe7d852.webp?t=1764335934\" width=626 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梦之投影是一款迷人又温馨的解谜游戏，专注于轻松休闲的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/5f05fc750c598f57cc3eb2564ae1d971.avif?t=1764335934\" width=600 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/76b4fd3dcadf8ab097293c669fe7d852.webp?t=1764335934\" width=626 height=38 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验动人故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与珊卡一同踏上旅程，沉浸在暖心而无言的故事中，聆听夏夜的蝉鸣，珍藏纯真的友谊，感受离别的悲喜交织。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/7ed7fcac29abe2c11254a101be58e267.poster.avif?t=1764335934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/7ed7fcac29abe2c11254a101be58e267.webm?t=1764335934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/7ed7fcac29abe2c11254a101be58e267.mp4?t=1764335934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/76b4fd3dcadf8ab097293c669fe7d852.webp?t=1764335934\" width=626 height=38 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样解谜方法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在桌面上旋转、摆放和堆叠各种物品，使其投影完美贴合墙上的剪影轮廓。发挥你的创造力吧！解谜方法无限，只要投影与轮廓匹配即可，更有众多成就待你解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/2f6b949cae14281bc22ec704e7438b85.poster.avif?t=1764335934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/2f6b949cae14281bc22ec704e7438b85.webm?t=1764335934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/2f6b949cae14281bc22ec704e7438b85.mp4?t=1764335934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/76b4fd3dcadf8ab097293c669fe7d852.webp?t=1764335934\" width=626 height=38 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索场景氛围</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不断变化的房间中寻找玩具，重温美好童年回忆。在 Floris Demandt 创作的舒缓旋律中，感受每一次奇妙的新发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/0842c167157130159122feca8a11069d.poster.avif?t=1764335934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/0842c167157130159122feca8a11069d.webm?t=1764335934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/0842c167157130159122feca8a11069d.mp4?t=1764335934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318800/extras/76b4fd3dcadf8ab097293c669fe7d852.webp?t=1764335934\" width=626 height=38 /></span></p>",
